# Inbox — {{MODULE_NAME}}

<!--
  This file receives messages delivered by `sync` from sibling modules and the parent.
  sync writes here; the module session reads here. The module session may mark entries
  as read or archived, but never deletes — rotation is handled by age-based policy
  (see references/module-communication.md §retention-and-rotation).

  Read flow (see references/parent-module-handoff.md §module-resume-mode Step 5):
    1. On resume, CoS reads this file under "## Unread".
    2. For each unread entry, CoS surfaces subject + tags + priority to the user.
    3. The user decides: act on it, mark read, or defer.
    4. CoS moves actioned entries to "## Read" with a dated marker.

  DO NOT edit message bodies. Append new status markers at the end of the entry.
-->

